-- Jets' Braylon Edwards Is Arrested for Drunk Driving, New York Post Reports
-- B y   J a y   B e b e r m a n
-- 2010-09-21T13:00:39Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-09-21/jets-braylon-edwards-is-arrested-for-drunk-driving-new-york-post-reports.html
New York Jets wide receiver Braylon
Edwards was arrested and charged with driving while intoxicated
after police stopped his car this morning in Manhattan, the New
York Post reported, citing police. 